{"tid":1468051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重開！！搵到解決內鬼既方法","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:44:02.000Z","uid":168969,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"09909eca0221f388ce4b2f657a1d15fe3f673b28","tid":1468051,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"捉到內鬼 冇搞事 冇傷害人既 可以係記者面前邀請佢走<br />\n<br />\n捉到搞事既 可以用適當既武力制服佢 唔洗打佢（我知大家都好嬲）制服完佢 係時候要交個波俾對家拆彈 佢做唔做野 全香港人睇住 記者影底晒 唔做野佢死緊 會觸發更多人不滿<br />\n<br />\n將自己代入執法者既角色 自然拆到內鬼既問題 最重要係得民心<br />\n<br />\n要話俾人知<br />\n佢地控制唔到情緒 我地控制到<br />\n佢地唔做既野 我地做到<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭係唔會講大話架！！！"},{"pid":"8f3e9d2b09872864c6da8dfd1d5132da253802e3","tid":1468051,"uid":167928,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"無論和理非定勇武 必須遵守<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 不打記者 <br />\n2. 不打救護<br />\n3. 不濫用酷刑 <br />\n4. 不攻擊平民</span></span>"},{"pid":"62f6e00cf63ef00a0fafe930b1700891797ae48c","tid":1468051,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:16.000Z","msg":"幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492ea252f80a71d7e64ad78461719f07df9cf68e","tid":1468051,"uid":302475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:12.000Z","msg":"而家係打輿論戰既時候！！！<br />\n得罪講句 捉到公安都唔識用 係咪抵輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1465595/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1465595/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"830cc3d199d9ab8062f27eb1c84f6c4ce4286667","tid":1468051,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c00188a9a1eecc251de9521e06a4cbe8146696cd","tid":1468051,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48e6f98585587ec0347a7d7e92e35e70a7b91ff0","tid":1468051,"uid":2757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":